message.body: Lindsey! What are you up to tomorrow late afternoon? I'm meeting a friend at 2, should be free and in the hood around 4...late coffee? Early cocktail?
Yes yes! Please! Just text me when you are through and we will find a good place to go! So looking forward to catching up!
Yay! Me too. Could be closer to 5, is that cool? I'll let you know when we're wrapping up
That sounds great! I have dinner with a friend around 7:30 but other than that, I'm free as a bird!
Perrrrfect! I've got a dinner thing too. We'll be in between buddies :-)
Hey you! Wrapping up early in no Philly, headed west. What's up wichu?
Hi!! I'm just at home, was gonna run to the co-op in a few! Wanna meet somewhere on Baltimore? What's your favorite spot?
Oh I love it all! Satellite? I'm taking the long way across town so I will be there in a bit
Yay!! Cool. I'll probably be there in 30 minutes or so!!! I'll see you then.
